These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, entrepreneur, mechanic, paramedic, photographer, social-worker, videographer
There are 7 different favourite colors: orange, fuchsia, purple, grey, apricot, red, azure
 1. the paramedic is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 2. the person who likes apricot is the paramedic##1
 3. the videographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
 4. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 5. the mechanic is in the middle##1
 6. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1
 7. the photographer is the person who likes orange##1
 8. the electrician is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 9. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
10. the person who likes grey is on the left of the mechanic##1
11. the videographer is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | photographer | paramedic | entrepreneur | mechanic | electrician | social-worker | videographer |
| Color   | orange    | apricot   | grey      | red | purple    | fuchsia    | azure         |

