.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: spanish, nigerian, pakistani, italian, canadian, german, dutch
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, funk, gospel, pop, punk, rock, soul
 1. the fan of punk is the italian##1
 2. the german is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 3. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
 4. the nigerian is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 5. the italian is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the german is on the left of the dutch##1
 7. the fan of punk is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the right of the canadian##1
 9. the fan of soul is on the left of the pakistani##1
10. the italian is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Nationality          | spanish | nigerian | canadian | italian | german | dutch | pakistani |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | gospel   | pop   | punk      | d&b       | soul       | rock     |

