 3. the nigerian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
 7. the egyptian is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the indonesian##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the thai is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire    | family     | comedy     | thriller      | mystery | zombie      | scientific     |
| Nationality   | indian | egyptian | nigerian | indonesian | thai | australian | argentine |

