.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
7 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, poker, canasta, monopoly, go, domino
7 different pets are kept: dog, fish, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig, horse, snake
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person playing go##1
 6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 8. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 9. the person playing canasta is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Game   | mah-jongg | poker | go     | canasta | domino | monopoly | bridge |
| Pet     | snake   | frog    | guinea-pig | horse     | dog         | goldfish     | fish        |

