.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-13::.
7 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit, ferret, fish, hedgehog, frog, snake
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, family, martial-arts, musical, romance, sports
 1. the person watching disaster movies is the owner of the ferret##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 4. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the person watching family movies is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
| Pet         | frog | rabbit   | snake | goldfish | hedgehog | fish | ferret  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts  | musical | sports  | family | romance | crime     | disaster |

